              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "The Concierge will run any non-blocked command without asking. If a malicious issue or repo file tricks the agent (prompt injection), it could delete files or leak data with no approval step. Only turn this on for repos and workspaces you fully trust.",
