              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Soleur runs commands automatically to get work done. It always blocks clearly dangerous commands (curl, wget, sudo, …) and hides your secrets — but no blocklist is perfect. A command that looks safe could still change or delete files in this workspace. Your work is backed up in git, and you can watch every command run in the chat. Only connect repos and accounts you trust.",
